    .container
      .row.heading
        .col-md-12
          h2 Bounty UNILOT
      .row.content
        .col-md-12
          h4 Official unilot.io bounty campaign terms:
          p UNILOT ICO starts on #[strong January 10, 2017] and we are happy to announce the official unilot.io bounty program details.
          p The total bounty program pool will amount to #[strong 3%] of all tokens sold during the pre-ICO and ICO stages.
          p If the number of bounty participants will be less than #[strong 250] active users - total bounty pool will be reduced to 1%. Active user - the person who made at least one activity in bounty program.

          h4 The Unilot.io total bounty pool will be divided as follows:
          ol
            li Bitcointalk — 20%
            li Translation and community management — 10%
            li Facebook — 10%
            li Twitter — 10%
            li Youtube — 6%
            li Reddit — 3%
            li Telegram — 10%
            li Mass media and Blogs — 17%
            li LinkedIn — 4%
            li Exclusive support — 5%
            li Reserve — 5%

          h4 Bounty payment
          p Payment is made only in Unilot.io tokens – UNILOT
          p Bounty program’s results, including the calculation of tokens earned, will be announced within one week after the token launch end date and time.
          p Each member's amount of bounty UNILOT tokens will be calculated using the following formula below.
          p 
            b
              i (Total amount of bounty campaign UNILOT tokens /  Total amount of bounty campaign participants' stakes)  *  Member's stakes
          p For example, the distribution of tokens in the signature campaign:
          p 
            i (Total amount of signature campaign UNILOT tokens /  Total amount of bounty signature campaign participants' stakes)  *  Member's stakes

          h4 Links
          ul
            li Website: #[a(href="https://unilot.io" target="_blank") https://unilot.io]
            li White Paper: #[a(href="https://unilot.io/en-us/white-paper" target="_blank") https://unilot.io/en-us/white-paper]
            li Official crowd sale thread on Bitcointalk: #[span.todo link]

          h4 Social media
          ul
            li Facebook: #[a(href="https://www.facebook.com/unilot.io/" target="_blank") https://www.facebook.com/unilot.io/]
            li Twitter: #[a(href="https://twitter.com/unilot_platform" target="_blank") https://twitter.com/unilot_platform]
            li Telegram: #[a(href="https://t.me/unilot_channel" target="_blank") https://t.me/unilot_channel]
            li Steemit: #[a(href="https://steemit.com/@unilot" target="_blank") https://steemit.com/@unilot]

          h4 How to join
          p Sign up on our official website of a bounty program: #[a(href="https://unilot.io/en-us/cp/sign-up.html" target="_blank") https://unilot.io/en-us/cp/sign-up.html] and find the mass media, blog posts, Steemit, Golos bounty campaign. If you have any questions regarding the bounty program, please use:
          ol.numbered
            li Steemit invite link – #[a(href="https://steemit.com/@unilot" target="_blank") https://steemit.com/@unilot]
              p Just sign in to send a message to our channel #Unilot.io_bounty to discuss the details.
            li Telegram chat – #[a(href="https://t.me/Uniloteng" target="_blank") https://t.me/Uniloteng]
            li For special offers – #[a(href="mailto:bounty@unilot.io" target="_blank") bounty@unilot.io]


      .row.heading
        .col-md-12
          h2 Bitcointalk
          p #[strong 20% of Total Bounty Pool] will be allocated for signature and avatar campaign participants.
      .row.content
        .col-md-12
          h4 Bounty:
          ol.numbered
            li Member: 1 Stake / Week
            li Full Member: 1.5 Stakes / Week
            li Sr. Member: 1.75 Stakes / Week
            li Hero Member: 2 Stakes / Week
            li Legendary: 2.5 Stakes / Week
          
          h4 Bonuses:
          p +0.25 stakes per week, if you use Unilot.io avatar + Unilot.io personal text.

          h4 Unilot.io avatar link: 
          p.todo link

          h4 Rules:
          ul.bulleted
            li Keep the signature (as well as the avatar and the personal text if you picked them as well) till the end of campaign. We will check your messages on a regular basis to make sure you are using our signature (and avatar and personal text, if applicable) at all times.
            li Only posts in the alternate cryptocurrencies sections of Bitcointalk are required and counted.
            li Make at least 10 quality posts in a week to be eligible for a reward. Your first week is 7 days starting from the date of approval (see the spreadsheet); your second week is the next 7 days, and so on.
            li Using multiple signatures at the same time is prohibited, only Unilot.io signature.
            li You are not allowed to use any other project’s avatar or personal text.
            li You must update the signature, the personal text, and the avatar immediately upon our request.
            li You must make sure that the signature you are wearing corresponds to your current rank at all times. When your account gets promoted to a higher rank during your participation, you must upgrade the signature.
            li Posts must be constructive and on-topic. Spam, low-quality posts, copypaste, and off-topic posts are strictly prohibited. Users found doing so will be immediately and permanently disqualified, reported to Bitcointalk moderators, and banned from any other bounty campaign.
            li Eligible posts must be at least 50 characters long.
            li We recommend keeping your signature till the final spreadsheet gets updated with your final post count (allow at least one week to count posts). Removing signature before post count may lead to your disqualification.
          p Unilot.io reserves the right to change the terms or apply new ones at any time at its sole discretion.

          h4 How to join
          ol.numbered
            li Sign up on our official website of the bounty program: #[a(href="https://unilot.io/en-us/cp/sign-up.html" target="_blank") https://unilot.io/en-us/cp/sign-up.html] and make a request for the participation in the Signature and avatar campaign bounty.
            li Add the Unilot.io signature campaign BBCode matching your account rank to the Signature field of your Bitcointalk profile.
            li We'll review your request and contact you to discuss the details or confirm your participation.

          h4 Questions?
          p If you have any questions regarding the signature and avatar bounty campaign, please use the Unilot.io Steemit for the communication.
          ol.numbered
            li Unilot.io Steemit invite link: #[span.todo ________]
            li Or use our Telegram chat – #[a(href="https://t.me/Uniloteng" target="_blank") https://t.me/Uniloteng]
            li For special offers – #[a(href="mailto:bounty@unilot.io" target="_blank") bounty@unilot.io]

