          p
            strong Standard (For users who have at least 300 and not more 1&nbsp;000 followers)
          ul.bulleted
            li 1 post about Unilot.io with a link to the official website – 1 Stake.
            li 1 like and 1 repost of 1 post from the official page of Unilot.io on Facebook – 1 Stake.
          p 
            strong Medium (For users who have at least 1&nbsp;001 and not more than 2&nbsp;000 followers)
          ul.bulleted
