            li Your Facebook account must have at least 300 real followers.
            li You have to like and repost at least 5 posts from our Facebook account: #[a(href="https://www.facebook.com/unilot.io/" target="_blank") https://www.facebook.com/unilot.io/]. Only 1 like + 1 repost per day will count.
            li You have to make 3 Facebook posts about Unilot.io in a week, include hashtag #[strong #Unilot.io]. Only 1 post per day will count.
            li You cannot remove your posts, likes or reposts you made within the framework of this Facebook bounty campaign until its end plus one week. This will make sure you quickly pass all checks.

